# Keep local build artifacts and secrets out of every image's build context (B3): smaller/faster
# context transfer, and `COPY apps/web/ …` can't drag a host node_modules/dist into the image.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.venv
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
.git
.github
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/*.db
**/.pytest_cache
**/.ruff_cache
**/coverage
apps/web/src-tauri/target
